cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.IT 

The paper discusses the use of deep reinforcement learning for managing energy-harvesting IoT nodes, which involves both machine learning and networking concepts. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a likely category. Finally, the paper discusses the use of reward functions and optimization, which falls under the category of cs.IT (Information Theory).
